{"lemma":"خاصٌّ","slug":"خاصٌّ","root":"خ.ص.ص","root_slug":"خ-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ص-ص","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10745","n10834"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"special"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"particular"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"specific"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"designated (بِ (bi) for)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"characteristic (بِ (bi) of)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"distinguished"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"private"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"exclusive"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of خَصَّ (ḵaṣṣa, “to favor, to endow, to be characteristic of, to concern”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10745","headword_ar":"خَاصٌّ","root":"xS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Particular; peculiar; special; distinct,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinguished, from others; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAm~N","text_ar":"عَامٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) ―         -b2-  [And hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Choice; select."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pare; unmixed; unadulterated."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b4-  [Used as a subst.,] it is syn. with ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAS~apN","text_ar":"خَاصَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Ks, Msb, K;) in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a corroborative; (Msb;) and which signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Distinguished people; persons of distinction;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinguished sort; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAm~apN","text_ar":"عَامَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) or the former is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAm~N","text_ar":"عَامٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓ the latter is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAm~apN","text_ar":"عَامَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [the pl. of both is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaAS~N","text_ar":"خَوَاصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiS~aAnN","text_ar":"خِصَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuS~aAnN","text_ar":"خُصَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, accord. to rule, the first of these is pl. only of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAS~apN","text_ar":"خَاصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and judging from other instances, we should regard the second and third as more probably pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAS~N","text_ar":"خَاصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but however the case may be,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiS~aAnN","text_ar":"خِصَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaAS~u","text_ar":"خَوَاصُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and so is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuS~aAnN","text_ar":"خُصَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxaAS~u waAlEaAm~u","text_ar":"الخَاصُّ وَالعَامُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlEam~apu","text_ar":"وَالعَمَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxaAS~apu","text_ar":"الخَاصَّةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The distinguished and the common people; the persons of distinction and the vulgar."},{"kind":"text","text":"] You also say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~amaA yafoEalu h`*aA xiS~aAnN","text_ar":"اـِنَّمَا يَفْعَلُ هٰذَا خِصَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"مِنَ النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaAS~u minohumo","text_ar":"خَوَاصُّ مِنْهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Only distinguished persons of mankind do this"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b5-  [It seems to be also, in some instances,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAS~apN","text_ar":"خَاصَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A particular, peculiar,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"special, friend, intimate, familiar, companion, associate, attendant, dependent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"servant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the latter is explained in the T [and JK] as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person whom thou hast appropriated, particularly distinguished, taken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chosen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotaSaSotahu","text_ar":"اِخْتَصَصْتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a friend,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for, thyself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [and it is used as a sing. and as a pl.: for] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA xaAS~atiY","text_ar":"هٰذَا خَاصَّتِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is my particular,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"special,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choicest, friend,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo xaAS~atiY","text_ar":"هُمْ خَاصَّتِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are my particular,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"peculiar,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"special,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choicest, friends,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (A.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN xaAS~N lifulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ خَاصٌّ لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kull p. 174,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bifulaAnK","text_ar":"بِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in the L,) [app. meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lifulaAnK","text_ar":"لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", unless it be mistranscribed, and the latter be the correct reading, which I think much the more probable;] i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one belongs exclusively"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a particular,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"peculiar,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"special, friend,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxaS~N","text_ar":"مُخَصٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (L.) ―         -b6-  See the dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAS~apN","text_ar":"خَاصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (namely"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuwayoS~apN","text_ar":"خُوَيْصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) below."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n10834","headword_ar":"خَاصٍ","root":"xSY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[act. part. n. of 1]. They say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a kaxaASiY","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ كَخَاصِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEayori","text_ar":"العَيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came like the gelder of the ass"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he came ashamed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwj","text_ar":"جوج"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disappointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsuccessful."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in that art.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":753}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%B5/","headword_ar":"خاص","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23235#0d67d9","body_html":"<span>الخاص: عبارة عن التفرد يقال: فلان خص بكذا، أي أفرد به ولا شركة للغير فيه.</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23235#be1edc","body_html":"<span>الخاص: هو كل لفظ وضع لمعنى معلوم على الانفراد المراد بالمعنى الذي وضع له اللفظ عينًا كان أو عرضًا، وبانفراد اختصاص اللفظ بذلك المعنى، وإنما قيده بالانفراد ليتميز عن المشترك.</span>"}]}}